A perfect stay
I really enjoyed my stay at A La Carte, Da-nang. The best part about the hotel was the staff/employees. Friendly, helpful and most spoke excellent English. We decided to organise our trips through the hotel and the help was great, they provided us a really good service. The food was really good and really well priced. The breakfast buffet was outstanding. The rooftop swimming pool was a great place to relax and it even has a rooftop bar to chill out at night. A small coffee shop with freshly made cakes on the bottom floor provided a nice place to chill out and relax prior to checking into our apartment. This was defiantly in my top 10 places I have stayed. My only grumble, if I have to add one, was there was a new hotel getting constructed opposite which did disturb my…
