Jel86 wrote a review Apr 2019
Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam1152 contributions150 helpful votes
+1
Great 4 star hotel on the beach
We loved our stay there. 2 nights. Spacious room with kitchen area. View to the beach on the side. The infinity pool on the rooftop is great and scenic. The rooftop bar could improve its offer and the quality of its drinks. The breakfast buffet offers a wide variety but noting is very good. The staff is very professional and lovely. Nice beach just across the street. Great value for money. We will be back.
