Unique and spectacular wedding venue
We are American expats living in Da Nang and chose A La Carte as the location for our wedding ceremony and reception in March, 2019. We used ALC's beautiful rooftop lounge and outdoor space overlooking the ocean for our 30-guest ceremony and 90-guest reception. From the moment we first met with the A La Carte Sales and Food & Beverage Team, to the follow-up after our event, every interaction and every detail exceeded our expectations. I cannot imagine that there is a more professional, kind, attentive, and all-around lovely team than those at A La Carte. A special shout out goes to Lucy, Nhat, Thao, and Tram! From the clear and timely communication with the superb sales team, to the quality of the food, attention to detail in the seating and music setup, to a thousand small…
